    <h3 class="title"><a href="/battlestar/story-bsg-god-gog#comment-9784" class="active">&quot;Lost&quot; episode analyses?</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by tichtich (not verified) on Wed, 2009-05-27 03:10.</div>
    <div class="content"><p>This is off-topic, I'm afraid, but I couldn't think of a better place to post it.</p>
<p>I've really enjoyed reading Brad's analyses of BSG. So, now that I've just started watching "Lost", season 5, I'm hoping to find a blog that does for Lost what Brad did for BSG. Does anyone have any suggestions? I'm looking for intelligent analyses, not discussion forums, synopses, trivia, etc. It doesn't matter if the whole season has been written up already, so long as I can avoid spoilers by reading them in sequence.</p>
</div>
    <div class="links">&raquo; <ul class="links"><li class="first last comment_reply"><a href="/comment/reply/914/9784" class="comment_reply">reply</a></li>
</ul></div>
