    <div class="content"><p>Why has this prophecy not been explained? How did Kara Thrace lead the Human race to its end? The original Kara did no such thing, and the "dead\angel" Kara provided the jump coordinates to our earth.  Its not clear whether the colonies population died out before integrating with earth tribes, but surely the "human" race continued to exist.  So what's the deal with the prophecy that "Kara Thrace will lead the human race to its end"?</p>
